Class AirlinerAircraft

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.aircrafts.Aircraft
      • by.zyablov.airlinecompany.beans.aircrafts.AirlinerAircraft
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>

    public class AirlinerAircraft
extends Aircraft
    Class AirlinerAircraft represents an airliner aircraft, AirlinerAircraft is a child of Aircraft, add a new field airlinerTechData, which represents an unique technical characteristic of every CargoAircraft object.
